---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Careers | Lau Hairdressing, Maidstone"
  description="Join the Lau Hairdressing team in Maidstone. Opportunities for students starting their career and experienced stylists looking for a new challenge."
>
  <div class="page-top">
    <section class="section section--light">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="page-title text-light mb-1">Current Vacancies</h1>
        <h2 class="subheading text-bold mb-3"><strong>It's all about the people</strong></h2>

        <p class="seo-content__text mb-4">Lau Hairdressing can offer you a fantastic opportunity to develop yourself as an individual, having fun with the satisfying knowledge that you are creating a real career and not just a job. So, if you're thinking about a career in this fantastic industry and want to know more about it, then get in touch today.</p>

        <div class="callout-box mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-bold mb-1">Students</h3>
          <h4 class="subheading text-bold mb-2">Our Future Professionals</h4>
          <p>We are always looking for enthusiastic people to join our team. If you are self motivated, passionate about fashion, have an artistic flair and feel ready to create your own future? Then you should consider a career with Lau Hairdressing. Don't be fooled, it's not going to be easy but it's definitely going to be worth it!</p>
          <p class="mb-3">Please email us in confidence to see if there are any current vacancies.</p>
          <a href="/contact.html" class="btn btn--outline">Enquire</a>
        </div>

        <div class="callout-box mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-bold mb-1">Experienced Stylists</h3>
          <h4 class="subheading text-bold mb-2">Are you an Experienced Stylist?</h4>
          <p class="mb-3">Do you need a new challenge with a great established company? To enquire if we have any current vacancies available, please contact our salon manager in complete confidence with your current C.V. If not now, we may do in the very near future. We look forward to your contact.</p>
          <a href="/contact.html" class="btn btn--outline">Enquire</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
